# Level 2 - Task 1: Calculator

## Project Title
Simple Web Calculator

## Objective
The objective of this project is to design a simple calculator that performs basic arithmetic operations using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## Description
This project is a web-based calculator that allows users to perform basic arithmetic calculations such as addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division. The interface is designed to be simple and user-friendly.

## Features
- Addition
- Subtraction
- Multiplication
- Division
- Clear display function

